title: Knesset Cancels Draft Law Talks
body: Prime Minister Binyamin Netanyahu called an urgent meeting with the Knesset's Foreign Affairs and Defense Committee chairman after the committee canceled all meetings on the proposed Draft Law due to disputes with chareidi lawmakers.

title: Rav Yisroel Mantel Relocates
body: Rav Yisroel Mantel, longtime mara d'asra of Khal Adath Jeshurun, will leave the Washington Heights synagogue after 19 years to relocate to Gateshead, England.
